Definition: a press conference or interview in which a government official explains to reporters the background of an action or policy
Example: the secretary gave us a backgrounder on public health issues
Synonyms: noun, cognition, background, press_conference, a, press, conference, or, interview, in, which, government, official, explains, to, reporters, the, of, an, action, policy, secretary, gave, us, on, public, health, issues
Category: noun.communication
